channel.title: [Approved] New Organisation Identifier: XI-IATI-AJS
channel.description:
The following addition to the IATI Organisation Identifier list has been proposed for the Associations des Juristes Sénégalaises (AJS).
No suitable registration code or agency has been found for this organisation.
**Code:** XI-IATI-AJS
**Name:** Associations des Juristes Sénégalaises (AJS)
**Description:** The Association des Juristes Sénégalaises (AJS) is an association of women lawyers who promote and contribute to the protection of the rights of individuals, particularly women and children.
**URL:** **[http://www.femmesjuristes.org](http://www.femmesjuristes.org/)**
If no objection is received this XI-IATI code will be approved and added in a week.
